largest and most strategic Fortress clients, Canyon Club. The property
transitioned from Shift4 to CardConnect and went live on August 1st with
approximately 15 venues installed. There are 80 locations in total.

The following issues have been reported:

•	 Terminals are randomly kicking users-out while in use.
•	 Tip adjustment does not total correctly.
•	 When adjusting tips, the entire amount is showing as one lump sum
    on settlement report instead of by individual EDC.
•	 The batch process is hard-closing several times a day, forcing all
    bartenders to log-out and log back in on all terminals which
    causes disruption of service.
•	 Bartenders can't clock-in or clock-out.
•  Property is experiencing continuous time-out, forcing staff to
    reboot the terminals several times a day.
